  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">BG Loan 2 Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed financing by IFC will support the growth of Banco General&apos;&apos;s low and middle income mortgage portfolio.  The project will support Panama&apos;&apos;s economic development as more families will be able to obtain mortgage financing given the Bank&apos;&apos;s extensive reach and the market segment that it is serving.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed project consists of a credit line of up to U$100 million for up to 5 years to Banco General (the Bank) to be used to fund lending activity in the low income mortgage sector.</narrative>
  </description>
